reviewText: i started using this video after my delivery four months ago and am really glad i tried it...the pace is perfect and the stability ball really is a great tool for variety. This video has great modifications for various levels of intensity. I really recommend getting her new FitToTheCore videos, Burn and Chisel, they are absolutely outstanding and can really get you into top shape.

reviewText: i loved this video, the stability ball is new to me but i truly loved doing the ab  work this way. Hart is the abs guru from the Abs of Steel videos, and she knows her stuff. This routine goes slowly and gives the muscles time to feel the effort you have to put into each exercise. It's a beginner tap, which i needed, and i think you can do some variations to this to get more out of it if you needed to. This is a great abs tape and I hgihly recommend it to get started, she is the best instructor.
summary: great abs routine, stability ball is easy to get use to
